            Sound editor for the Casio CZ101 & CZ1000

              This programe will only run in MED RES

Will need FAST BASIC and will only run on a 520ST when FAST  BASIC 
                        is on a CARTRIDGE 

Also on 520 ST No ACCESSORIES can be loaded indeed it is best to 
boot up with the DESKTOP file suppled on the disk

Enter FAST BASIC in normal way. Then load CZ101.BSC and run
Sometimes  you may get a memory error just try and rerun a  couple 
of times if this fails then reboot.

This program will allow you to create sounds for your Casio 
synthesizer on the screen using the mouse. These sounds can be 
stored on disc as single sounds or as a bank of 16. You should be 
able to store around 500 individual sounds on one single sided 
disc and around 1080 on a double sided disc.These sounds can 
easily down loaded to the synthesizer, again as a single sound or
asabankof16.Soundsmayalsobeloadedupfromthesynthesizer
alteredandstoredetc. 

               CZ101.BCS
               MENU.DAT
               CZ101PIC.PI2
